{
  "texts": [
    "Using the tool classes written according to rules and query logic, a large amount of knowledge is efficiently written into the knowledge graph.",
    "We select the travel topic knowledge graph as the construction instance, and the display effect is shown in the Fig. 4.",
    "The \"Travel\" is divided into two categories: \"Era\" and \"Resource\".",
    "The \"Era\" is divided into two parts: \"History\" and \"Modern\", among which \"Folk Custom\", \"Religion\", \"Traditional Chinese Opera\", \"Minority Culture\", \"Painting and Calligraphy Art\" and \"Landscape Architecture\" all belong to the \"History\", while \"Contemporary Art\", \"Popular Art\", \"Natural Science\", \"Film and Television\" and \"Modern Architecture\" all belong to the \"Modern\".",
    "Meanwhile, the \"Resource\" is divided into two parts: \"Natural Landscape\" and \"Artificial Facility\"."
  ]
}